						               													<description>A simple and elegant turn based racing game based on Racetrack, that teaches optimal racing lines, simple mathematics and physics in a fun way.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Race in the Solo Campaign and climb your way from the F3 League for new talents, to the F1 League with the professionals, or invite your friends for a multiplayer challenge for up to 4 players on one of the 10 different tracks included in the game. Customize the game by creating your own tracks, adding alternative rules and making your own league. Learn how to drive in the Tutorial and make use of the powerful upgrades to become the best Formula One driver! By using the grid intersection points, you move your car according to specific movement rules. The grid and track size is adjusted to a perfect combination of difficulty and time spent racing. One lap is typically finished in 5-10 minutes per player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Download the game in the Files section: Grid Racer - Formula One (Digital Edition)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;The Digital Edition is optimized for digital note taking devices with a stylus, such as Onyx Boox, Ratta Supernote, reMarkable, Apple iPad, etc, that are able to annotate on top of the PDF file and follow internal linking for a smoother gameplay experience. You may also Print and Play it.&amp;quot; - Designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
